  "solution": {
    "answer": "$H_0(S^2) \\cong \\mathbb{Z},\\quad H_2(S^2) \\cong \\mathbb{Z},\\quad H_n(S^2) = 0 \\text{ otherwise.}$",
    "steps": [
      "CW structure: one 0-cell $v$ and one 2-cell $e^2$ (attached by the constant map $S^1 \\to v$). No 1-cells.",
      "Cellular chain complex: $0 \\to \\mathbb{Z} \\xrightarrow{d_2} 0 \\xrightarrow{d_1} \\mathbb{Z} \\to 0$.",
      "All boundary maps are zero (since $C_1 = 0$ and the attaching map is degree 0).",
      "$H_2 = \\ker(d_2)/\\operatorname{im}(d_3) = \\mathbb{Z}/0 = \\mathbb{Z}$.",
      "$H_1 = 0/0 = 0$ (no 1-cells at all).",
      "$H_0 = \\mathbb{Z}$ (one connected component). All $H_n = 0$ for $n \\geq 3$."
    ]
  }
}
